Reviews.review: I bought this to add storage and shelf space to my kitchen. It holds my toaster, coffee maker, and blender on the shelf with enough room in between each.  The lower shelf is sturdy and holds my heavy electrolux stand mixer along with my heavy flour mill and a few other essentials. The lower most bottom shelf holds cutting boards and other low profile items. It comes with a wine glass rack but that took up too much space. The upper shelf is perfect for my canisters  and has room to spare. It is the perfect addition to my kitchen. I have had it for three years now and it is still as sturdy as the day I assembled it.  It was a cinch to assemble, and the shelving can be adapted somewhat as the height is determined by the placement of connector rings before adding the bars. It is a very nice addition for any kitchen.
Reviews.title: Easy to assemble, durable, clean lines

Reviews.review: This baker's rack was the perfect addition to my kitchen! I was looking for a microwave cart with extra storage. My microwave fits perfect on the "cutting board" shelf and allows me to store drinks, containers, etc. on the shelves below. The small rack on top holds my baking canisters and the hooks are great for utensils (or my car keys!). This is very easy to put together and requires no tools. I highly recommend purchasing this unit.
Reviews.title: You'll love this!

Reviews.review: We purchased this for our small kitchen in our apartment. It fits beautifully and does not take up too much space. It was very easy to put together- only took me about a half hour by myself. Very sturdy and nice looking! The bottom shelves hold our rather large microwave, coffee pot, juicer, ect. Wonderful piece!
Reviews.title: Great Purchase!

Reviews.review: Fits into a small space, but gives you TONS of storage and a surprisingly large feeling cutting board or work space. Very easy to put together, all shelves are easily adjustable for height and spacing, and the final product is lightweight whilst still feeling sturdy and stable. Highly recommend!
Reviews.title: Absolutely perfect

Reviews.review: Item arrived fast in good condition. Put it together on my own in about 20 mins. I added some hooks to the top rack to hang a few more pots and rack remains stable. Cutting board is a great height for kneading dough (I'm 5.4). I loaded up the lower racks with appliances and some of those plastic drawers to put odds and ends in. Has made a world of difference to the efficiency of my kitchen and freed up a lot of counter space. Have already recommended it to family.
Reviews.title: Strong and versatile

Reviews.review: I bought this to add storage to our kitchen. It was a bit heavy, but very easy to assemble. As we unpack, I will better utilize the space, but it seems quite sturdy and I love the fact that it holds a lot of weight, so I can use it to store my juicer and cast iron pots and pans.
Reviews.title: Great buy

Reviews.review: This bakers rack was extremely easy to put together, it looks great in our small breakfast nook kitchen and is very sturdy. I have no complaints! We love it!
Reviews.title: Great Space Saver and Stylish

Reviews.review: Took about 30 min to put together by myself!......love it! Its solid quality and saves so much space. Buy it!
Reviews.title: Sturdy and Compact

Reviews.review: Very easy to put together and fits the space perfectly. The cutting board looks very nice; I like the grooved pattern
Reviews.title: Exactly what I was looking for

Reviews.review: This product is ideal for a small narrow kitchen if you have the right wall to put it against (which I did). It was very simple to put together except that the wood board was a little difficult to get back into the rack. Still, a very good buy, very sturdy and looks nice without being frilly.
Reviews.title: good product
